  layout(
    xaxis = list(title = " "),
    yaxis = list(
      title = "US$ bilhões",
      tick0 = 0,
      dtick = 10
    )
  ) %>%
  rangeslider(thickness = 0.05)
```

### % do PIB
```{r}
