### Receita nominal de serviços (Gráfico) (Tx. acum. no ano) (%)
```{r}
plot_ly(
  data = pms_seg_acum_ano_rec, 
  x = ~date, 
  y = ~as.numeric(gsub(",", ".", `Total`)),
  type = "scatter",
  mode = "lines"
) %>%
  layout(
    xaxis = list(title = " "),
    yaxis = list(
      title = "%",
      tick0 = 0,
      dtick = 3
    )
  ) %>%
  rangeslider(thickness = 0.05)
```

